headline: RTX Corporation’s (RTX) Raytheon Wins New Contracts

headline: HII Secures Contract to Support USS Harry S. Truman Aircraft Carrier
summary: Huntington Ingalls lands a $97.7 million deal to support the refueling and complex overhaul of the USS Harry S. Truman, reinforcing its aircraft carrier dominance.
